{"tid":1727504,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"特務警察集中討論區，請唔好輕敵","createTime":"2019-11-16T12:55:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-19T06:07:58.000Z","uid":20416,"like":19,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"9065799b37c4878369323c698ccb9b2ee91ef5eb","tid":1727504,"uid":20416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T12:55:19.000Z","msg":"首先切記唔好<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">輕敵</span></span><br />\n請得呢一百人一定有佢地既role<br />\n懲教仲要自願做就一定深藍<br />\n落手一定超重<br />\n個人覺得佢地係負責專捉火魔等等<br />\n分分鐘比速龍更輕裝更敏捷<br />\n<br />\n個人建議：千其<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">唔好</span><br />\n試佢地一兩次先<br />\n摸清楚佢地既底 作用係乜<br />\n體能 裝備係點等等<br />\n打仗永遠都要摸清楚對手既底<br />\n<br />\n所以朋友們下次出黎<br />\n一定要打醒十二分精神<br />\nbe water <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">幫手推阿！</span>"},{"pid":"b1b09ffa2d2b68508c1d3c028a230fea0c75eb5b","tid":1727504,"uid":46042,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T12:55:50.000Z","msg":"聽個名諗起德國納粹時期秘密警察"},{"pid":"c7cfd56a693db99c97eaf205be84ca7868b6a56f","tid":1727504,"uid":61831,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T12:56:40.000Z","msg":"有機會係速龍級數<br />\n始終睇落似係CSD入面既精英"},{"pid":"23ab4f84a206e1bc5d263b7cff076cb1db67e1f1","tid":1727504,"uid":326261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T12:58:56.000Z","msg":"呢個要推"},{"pid":"c0c7c16391585821f9b487bcb1036c42a443d60e","tid":1727504,"uid":20416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c7cfd56a693db99c97eaf205be84ca7868b6a56f","tid":1727504,"uid":61831,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T12:56:40.000Z","msg":"有機會係速龍級數<br />\n始終睇落似係CSD入面既精英"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T12:59:16.000Z","msg":"應該輕裝過佢地"},{"pid":"96a0abeeb93b7d7ced48fdf121708e216e5ce8d4","tid":1727504,"uid":216002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T13:00:57.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n一定好撚打得 一個都敵到3個速龍"},{"pid":"d43c740c3c1056fb3a88ba14b8f3689329eea6