/lih.kg/1675545\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1675545</a><br />\n<br />\n眾籌link:  <a href=\"https://www.collaction.hk/project/story/1209\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.collaction.hk%2Fproject%2Fstory%2F1209&d=VpJPAaQEVg4A3L06AjdBQN%2BR0LtvndqJ8lr%2BzYsHiyM%3D&h=8356b081\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.collaction.hk/project/story/1209</a><br />\n官方link (我們香港人計劃) :<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.pori.hk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.pori.hk%2F&d=VpJPAaQEVg4A3L06AjdBQN%2BR0LtvndqJ8lr%2BzYsHiyM%3D&h=cd426514\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.pori.hk/</a><br />\n<br />\n(對唔住，咁危難時刻下我知而家仲叫大家課金可能好反感，但我相信兄弟爬山，各有各做，行得通就全力去做<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)"},{"pid":"7536c1a6cf4099155a8984bc45ebca6f2575fe7e","tid":1727504,"uid":122202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T13:15:51.000Z","msg":"懲教飛虎平時負責乜"},{"pid":"eb69f098b05bc6d9b8ac2f7cd4c954fd216ec7ba","tid":1727504,"uid":20416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7536c1a6cf4099155a8984bc45ebca6f2575fe7e","tid":1727504,"uid":122202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T13:15:51.000Z","msg":"懲教飛虎平時負責乜"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T13:21:16.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"feeaec305947e0200a9f19a81017e97f4c63a2f3","tid":1727504,"uid":53666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T13:49:32.000Z","msg":"等圍內爆料。"},{"pid":"6c3c4331e8e71983a59e7c4625450ab6b90db9fd","tid":1727504,"uid":338435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T15:28:33.000Z","msg":"懲教濫暴得更加嚴重<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba1b5c6e3c19be08a34500cf2f96e21dc3efd9e7","tid":1727504,"uid":20416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6c3c4331e8e71983a59e7c4625450ab6b90db9fd","tid":1727504,"uid":338435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-11-